cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  ACQUIRE 26.7.1: Taxonomy, Checklist and Reporting Templates for Reproducible
  In-the-Wild Sensing
message: >-
  If you use this framework, its taxonomy, or its checklist, please cite the
  accompanying paper (see preferred-citation) and state the artifact version.
  Thresholds and recipes change as evidence accumulates, so a version identifies
  exactly what a study was assessed against.
